data.description: Introducing your ideal urban retreat 900 S 94th St 1056, Chandler, AZ 85224 a pristine, three-level townhome, step inside & discover an open layout, the main level welcomes you with a spacious living area, ideal for relaxation & gatherings, the kitchen is well appointed with black appliances,  breakfast bar. Boasting 2 bedrooms & 2.5 bathrooms, each bedroom has an ensuite, one with a walk-in closet & the other with closet & storage space. Freshly painted, new carpet, this gem is move-in ready, inviting you to embrace a lifestyle of comfort & convenience. 2 car garage. This townhome offers 2 community pools & playgrounds, easy access to entertainment, major freeways, shopping districts, & an array of dining options, Chandler Fashion Square & the new Scheels for outdoor enthusiasts. Chandler is home to leading companies like Intel, NXP Semiconductors, Microchip Technology among others.  Minutes to the 202 Freeway, the 101 Freeway, close distance to the 10 and 60 Freeways.
